gameType.descr:
Contract type identifier (e.g., 'RPS', 'GUESS').
Used for CLI validation.

sessionIDCounter.descr: Global counter for generating unique session IDs.

methods.name: createSession
methods.desc:
Initializes a new game session with the provided configuration.
Validates the Minimum Balance Requirement (MBR) payment.

methods.name: registerPirate
methods.desc:
Allows a player to join the game during the registration phase.
Requires the player to cover their own data storage cost (MBR).

methods.name: proposeDistribution
methods.desc:
Submits a distribution proposal. Can only be called by the current proposer.
The distribution byte array must match the total pot amount.

methods.name: commitVote
methods.desc: Commits a hashed vote during the voting phase.

methods.name: revealVote
methods.desc:
Reveals a previously committed vote.
Updates the proposal vote count.

methods.name: executeRound
methods.desc:
Executes the current round logic after the reveal phase.
Determines if the proposal passed or failed.
Eliminates the proposer if failed, or proceeds to next round/victory.

methods.name: claimWinnings
methods.desc: Allows a pirate to claim their share of the pot after the game ends.

methods.name: getRequiredMBR
methods.desc: Calculates the MBR required for specific actions.

methods.name: timeOut
methods.desc:
Handles timeouts in various phases.
If registration stuck: refunds pirates.
If proposal stuck: eliminates the current proposer and moves to next round.

methods.name: initialize
methods.desc:
Sets the game type. Immutable once set.
Can only be called by the creator.
